high_descs: Turn around and face the stove in front of you.
Open the cabinet to the right of the stove, take out a brown bowl and close the cabinet.
Turn around around and face the fridge to your right.
Place the bowl in the fridge in front of you and take it out.
Turn left and face the sink in front of you.
Place the brown bowl in the cabinet below the sink in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold bowl in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: turn around and head to the table
pick up the bowl from the table
turn around and head to the fridge
place the bowl on cool in the fridge
turn around and head to the cupboard under the sink
place the bowl in the cupboard
anns.task_desc: place a cold bowl in the cupboard

high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter right of the stove.
Open the cabinet under the toaster on the counter, pick up the grey bowl in that cabinet.
Turn around, bring the bowl to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Bring the chilled bowl back to the sink on the left.
Open up the cabinet under the left sink and put the bowl in there.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl in the cabinet.
